  "description": "<p><strong>感谢<a href=\"http://www.99danji.com\" target=\"_blank\">99单机</a>的投递</strong><br /></p><p>国外达人Grahame近来矢志用创意积木游戏《我的世界》（Minecraft）来“重制”好莱坞经典科幻大片《星球大战：新希望》，不久前他在互联网上公布了其的首个工作成果——《我的世界》版的《星球大战》开场前15分钟。别说，看着科幻迷们熟悉的经典角色包括C3P0、R2D2、黑勋爵以及莉娅公主等人以像素方块人的面目出场，倒也颇为喜感。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2dd982f0/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242654.htm&amp;t=%E6%9C%89%E6%89%8D%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8A%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%80%8B%E7%89%88%E3%80%8A%E6%98%9F%E7%90%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98%E3%80%8B%E5%89%8D15%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242654.htm&amp;t=%E6%9C%89%E6%89%8D%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8A%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%80%8B%E7%89%88%E3%80%8A%E6%98%9F%E7%90%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98%E3%80%8B%E5%89%8D15%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242654.htm&amp;t=%E6%9C%89%E6%89%8D%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8A%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%80%8B%E7%89%88%E3%80%8A%E6%98%9F%E7%90%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98%E3%80%8B%E5%89%8D15%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242654.htm&amp;t=%E6%9C%89%E6%89%8D%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8A%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%80%8B%E7%89%88%E3%80%8A%E6%98%9F%E7%90%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98%E3%80%8B%E5%89%8D15%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.